flowchart TD
    A[Governed agent attempts visibility change] --> B{Target becomes public?}
    B -- No --> C[Allow private or internal save]
    B -- Yes --> D[Resolve acting governed agent]
    D --> E{Agreement accepted?}
    E -- No --> F[Block transition with publishing agreement error]
    E -- Yes --> G{Authorization still valid?}
    G -- No --> H[Block transition with authorization error]
    G -- Yes --> I[Persist public visibility state]
    I --> J[Public discovery surfaces can read record]

    subgraph Actors
      P[Person]
      R[Robot]
    end

    P --> D
    R --> D

    subgraph Enforcement Points
      V[Privacy validation]
      U[Publishable validation]
      N[Platform network visibility validation]
      T[MCP and request context]
    end

    D --> V
    D --> U
    D --> N
    D --> T
